---
layout: default
title: Speaking Events
description: An overview of all my talks, past and to come, including slides and videos.
keywords:
  - speaking
  - talks
  - conferences
permalink: /talks/
---

{% render "styles.liquid",
  inline: site.configuration.inline_assets,
  partials: "
    components/list,
    components/tags
  "
%}

{% markdown %}
Over the last few years I’ve had the amazing opportunity to be a speaker at some
great events. If you would like me to speak at your conference, be sure to get
in touch!
{% endmarkdown %}

<ul class="List">
  {% for event in speaking %}
  <li class="List__item">
    <span class="List__secondary-content">
      {{ event.date | time }} ❦ {{ event.location }}
    </span>
    <a href="{{ event.link }}" class="List__primary-content" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      {{ event.event }}
    </a>
    {% if event.actions %}
      <ul class="Tags">
        {% for action in event.actions %}
        <li class="Tag">
          <a class="Tag__link NoBackground" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="{{ action[1] }}">
            {{ action[0] }}</a>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      {% endif %}
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
